GET {{baseUrl}}/repair-order/67564bd079c348ec90835a71
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 更新工单状态(完工)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/repair-order/67564bd079c348ec90835a71/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "status": "completed",
    "actualCompletionTime": "{{$datetime iso8601}}"
}

